[267760.50036, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[3G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BIt'll be replayed through the brain next time the warehouse is\u001b[66Gwritable.\u001b[76G\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BBranc\u001b[9G remains \u001b[19Gpen — notes/memory\u001b[38Gauthoring\u001b[48Gand\u001b[52G\u001b[38;5;153mbranch_closed\u001b[66G\u001b[39mstay\u001b[71Gwith\u001b[76Gyou\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bper\u001b[7Gthe\u001b[11Gclose\u001b[17Gcontract.\r\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m✻\u001b[3GCogitated for 14m 31s\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[48;5;237m\u001b[38;5;239m❯ \u001b[38;5;231mare there any gotchas or improvements we should make note of and capture\u001b[39m      \r\u001b[1B\u001b[49m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B  \u001b[38;5;246mSearched for\u001b[16G\u001b[1m1\u001b[22m \u001b[20Gttern, l\u001b[29Gsted \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m directory, ran \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m shell command \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39m\u001b[1mWrite\u001b[22m(\u001b]8;id=uvx26x;file:///home/hades/clyffy/landing/study/t2/b/docs/BRAIN_SIGNAL_FOLD_NOTES.md\u0007docs/BRAIN_SIGNAL_FOLD_NOTES.md\u001b]8;;\u0007)\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;246m●\u001b[3G\u001b[39mRunning \u001b[1m1\u001b[22m shell command…\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[20;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
[267760.540545, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\u001b[38;5;246m  ⎿  \u001b[39mWrote\u001b[12G\u001b[1m53\u001b[15G\u001b[22mlines\u001b[21Gto\u001b[24G\u001b[1mdocs/BRAIN_SIGNAL_FOLD_NOTES.md\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[22m   \u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[2m  1 \u001b[22m# POST /signal/fold — gotchas & follow-ups (study-t2-adv)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B   \u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[2m  3 \u001b[22mContext: endpoint added to `interfaces/clyffy-brain` accepting t\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B   \u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[2m    \u001b[22myped fold signals over\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[2m    \u001b[22met: `cargo test -p\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m \u001b[3G   \u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[2m  5 \u001b[22mclyffy-brain` green, 0 warnings across engine/brain/CLI, engine \r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[2m  6 \r\u001b[1B\u001b[22m\u001b[39m     \u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[2m  7 \u001b[22m## Gotchas (grounded — each verified in-tree)\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[2m  9 \u001b[22m1. **`fold-signals.queue` has NO drainer.** `grep -r fold-signal\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39m   \u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[2m    \u001b[22ms.queue` across the\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[5C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;231m\u001b[2m    \u001b[22may's\r\u001b[1B\u001b[39m \u001b[3G   \u001b[38;5;246m… +69 lines \u001b[39m\u001b[K\u001b[23;1H\u001b[20;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
