[267816.342087, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bhook-traffic volume, wrong shape u\u001b[38Gder\u001b[42Gbursts.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B4.\u001b[6G\u001b[1mNo idempotency\u001b[21G\u001b[22m—\u001b[23Ga\u001b[25Gretried\u001b[33Gcurl\u001b[38Gor\u001b[41Gfuture\u001b[48Gqueue\u001b[54Greplay\u001b[61Gdouble-inserts;\u001b[77Gno\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsignal UUID or uniqueness constrai\u001b[38Gt.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mNon-gotcha worth noting:\u001b[22m validation is prop\u001b[47Grly single-sourced — the\u001b[72Gendpoint\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bparses\u001b[10Gvia th\u001b[17G \u001b[19Ghared \u001b[38;5;153mFromStr\u001b[39m impls in \u001b[38;5;153mclyffy-telemetry/src/fold.rs\u001b[39m,\u001b[72Gand\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;153mFoldPhase::ALL: [FoldPhase; 7]\u001b[34G\u001b[39mis\u001b[37Glength-checked\u001b[52Gat\u001b[55Gcompile\u001b[63Gtime,\u001b[69Gso\u001b[72Gthe\u001b[76G400\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\"legal set\" message can't drift\u001b[35Gwhen variants are \u001b[54Gdd\u001b[57Gd.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mImprovements queued in the doc:\u001b[22m boot-time queue dr\u001b[54Giner\u001b[59G(blocked on\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bidempo\u001b[10Gency),\u001b[17Gsignal\u001b[24GUUID\u001b[29G+\u001b[31Gconflict-ignore\u001b[47Gsemantics,\u001b[58G\u001b[38;5;153mspawn_blocking\u001b[73G\u001b[39maround\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bthe\u001b[7Gemit,\u001b[13Gand\u001b[17Gtest\u001b[22Ggaps\u001b[27G(unknown\u001b[36G\u001b[38;5;153mlane\u001b[39m/\u001b[38;5;153mengine\u001b[48G\u001b[39m400\u001b[52Gpaths,\u001b[59G\u001b[38;5;153msupersedes\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39mround-trip).\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1BEverything \u001b[15Gives \u001b[21Gn \u001b[38;5;153mdocs/BRAIN_SIGNAL_FOLD_NOTES.md\u001b[39m, and the \u001b[38;5;153mnotes_authored\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[39mfold signal is\u001b[18Gqueued. C\u001b[56G\u001b[38;5;153my-t2-adv\u001b[39m:\u001