[267817.021798, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bis the sharpest finding.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B2. \u001b[1mFresh worktrees have no \u001b[38;5;153mclyffy\u001b[39m binary\u001b[44G\u001b[22m—\u001b[46Ghooks\u001b[52Gfall\u001b[57Gback\u001b[62Gto\u001b[65Gthe\u001b[69Gqueue,\u001b[76Gwhich\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B(per #1) is currently a write-only hole. Fallback\u001b[53Gworks; replay doesn't\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bexist.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B3. \u001b[1mBlocking DuckDB insert on a tokio worker\u001b[22m — the\u001b[53G\u001b[38;5;153m/signal/fold\u001b[66G\u001b[39mhandler\u001b[74Gemits\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bstraight through the warehouse sink with no \u001b[38;5;153mspawn_blocking\u001b[39m. Fin\u001b[67G at\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bhook-traffic volume, wrong shape u\u001b[38Gder\u001b[42Gbursts.\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B4.\u001b[6G\u001b[1mNo idempotency\u001b[21G\u001b[22m—\u001b[23Ga\u001b[25Gretried\u001b[33Gcurl\u001b[38Gor\u001b[41Gfuture\u001b[48Gqueue\u001b[54Greplay\u001b[61Gdouble-inserts;\u001b[77Gno\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsignal UUID or uniqueness constrai\u001b[38Gt.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mNon-gotcha worth noting:\u001b[22m validation is prop\u001b[47Grly single-sourced — the\u001b[72Gendpoint\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bparses\u001b[10Gvia th\u001b[17G \u001b[19Ghared \u001b[38;5;153mFromStr\u001b[39m impls in \u001b[38;5;153mclyffy-telemetry/src/fold.rs\u001b[39m,\u001b[72Gand\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;153mFoldPhase::ALL: [FoldPhase; 7]\u001b[34G\u001b[39mis\u001b[37Glength-checked\u001b[52Gat\u001b[55Gcompile\u001b[63Gtime,\u001b[69Gso\u001b[72Gthe\u001b[76G400\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\"legal set\" message can't drift\u001b[35Gwhen variants are \u001b[54Gdd\u001b[57Gd.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mImprovements queued in t\u001b[56G\u001b[22mer\u001b[59G(blocked on\u001b[23;1H\u001b[20;3H\u001b[?25h\u001b[?2026l"]
