[268585.776822, "o", "\u001b[?2026h\u001b[?25l\u001b[H\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bexist.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B3. \u001b[1mBlocking DuckDB insert on a tokio worker\u001b[22m — the\u001b[53G\u001b[38;5;153m/signal/fold\u001b[39m handler emits\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bstraight\u001b[12Gthrough\u001b[20Gthe\u001b[24Gwarehouse\u001b[34Gsink\u001b[39Gwith\u001b[44Gno\u001b[47G\u001b[38;5;153mspawn_blocking\u001b[39m.\u001b[63GFine\u001b[68Gat\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bhook-traffic volume, wrong shape under bursts.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B4. \u001b[1mNo idempotency\u001b[22m — a retried curl or future queue replay doubl\u001b[67G-inserts;\u001b[77Gno\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bsignal UUID or uniqueness constrai\u001b[38Gt.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mNon-gotcha worth noting:\u001b[22m validatio\u001b[38G is\u001b[42Gproperly\u001b[51Gsingle-sourced\u001b[66G—\u001b[68Gthe\u001b[72Gendpoint\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bparses\u001b[10Gvia\u001b[14Gthe\u001b[18Gshared\u001b[25G\u001b[38;5;153mFromStr\u001b[33G\u001b[39mimpls\u001b[39Gin\u001b[42G\u001b[38;5;153mclyffy-telemetry/src/fold.rs\u001b[39m,\u001b[72Gand\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[38;5;153mFoldPhase::ALL: [FoldPhase; 7]\u001b[39m is length-ch\u001b[47Gcked at compile time, so\u001b[72Gthe 400\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\"legal\u001b[10Gset\" m\u001b[17Gs\u001b[19Gage can't drift when variants are added.\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1B\u001b[1mImprovements queued in the doc:\u001b[35G\u001b[22mboot-time queue dr\u001b[54Gin\u001b[57Gr (blocked\u001b[68Gon\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bidempotency),\u001b[17Gsignal\u001b[24GUUID\u001b[29G+\u001b[31Gconflict-ignore\u001b[47Gsemantics,\u001b[58G\u001b[38;5;153mspawn_blocking\u001b[73G\u001b[39maround\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bthe emit, and test gaps (unknown \u001b[38;5;153mlane\u001b[39m/\u001b[38;5;153mengine\u001b[39m 400 p\u001b[54Gths,\u001b[59G\u001b[38;5;153msupersedes\u001b[39m\u001b[K\r\u001b[2C\u001b[1Bround-\u001b[10Grip). \u001b[17G      \u001b[24